{"content":[{"id":"6ef08750","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"8b03aaa","settings":{"title":"Add Your Heading Text Here","editor":"<p data-path-to-node=\"1\"><strong>Product Description <\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">Step into elegance with this beautifully crafted Kurta suit set. The outfit boasts a contemporary silhouette and premium inner lining for maximum comfort during long events. Complete with a matching sharara pant and an embroidered dupatta, this ensemble is designed to make a statement at weddings and festive gatherings.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong>Top (Kurta)<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\">Fabric &amp; Lining: Made from heavy pure soft Fendy silk fabric paired with a pure microscrape full inner lining.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\">Work &amp; Details: Adorned with fancy embroidery sequence, dori, and zari work across the front and hemline.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\">Length &amp; Sizing: Features a top length of approximately 36 inches. Available in sizes XS(34), S(36), M(38), L(40), and XL(42).<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Bottom (Sharara)<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\">Fabric &amp; Fit: Tailored from pure Fendy silk fabric in a fully stitched free-size pattern.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\">Volume &amp; Flare: Features a generous, full flare of 1.5 + 1.5 meters for a dramatic ethnic look.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong>Wash Instructions <\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"6\">First Wash: Dry clean recommended to maintain the fabric texture and sequence work.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\">Subsequent Washes: Gentle hand wash separately in cold water using a mild liquid detergent.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">Care Advice: Do not wring or twist. Dry in shade away from direct sunlight to prevent color fading. Iron on low heat on the reverse side only.<\/p>"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"bzotech-heading-global","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"container"}],"se